data.description: Great Price on this level entry - NO STAIRS to this open concept 2 bedroom, 2 full bath, single level, corner unit condo with an attached garage in desirable Carrara. Extended ceilings, all new carpet and paint and filled with natural light - you can just move in!  Generously sized living room with fireplace, dining room with balcony access and kitchen with new garbage disposal, eating bar and direct access to the garage for security! Primary bedroom with full bath, double sinks and walk-in closet. All appliances including refrigerator, washer, dryer will convey. Walking distance to elementary school, shopping, restaurants and parks. Easy access to freeways, Lake Tapps and downtown Auburn. Inspection available after viewing upon request.
